---
title: St. Jean Baptiste Chômeur Pudding with Maple Syrup
description: You can’t go wrong with dessert, and this delectable Quebec treat with light, fluffy sponge baked in a delicious DIY maple sauce is no exception. Bonne Saint-Jean-Baptiste!
